er documents, \n\nphysician/allowed practitioner: progress notes, recent history and physical, discharge summary, orders, \nand consults. \n\no  Do not include diseases or conditions that have been resolved or do not affect the patient\u2019s current \n\nfunctional, cognitive, mood or behavior status; medical treatments; nurse monitoring; or risk of death at \nthe time of assessment.", "type": "Document"}}